<section class="hero">

<h2>Step Into Light. Walk in Truth.</h2>

<p>
WalkWay Kakuma is a Christ-centered outreach initiative serving communities in Kakuma and Kalobeyei Refugee Camps in Kenya. Through evangelism, prayer, home visitation, children outreach, and compassionate care, the ministry seeks to restore hope and strengthen faith among vulnerable individuals and families.
</p>

<a class="btn" href="#about">Learn More</a>

